267
00:20:25,516 --> 00:20:27,101
Kau tidak lihat?
/ Apa?

268
00:20:27,143 --> 00:20:30,271
Sesuatu melintasi jalan.
/ Tidak ada apa-apa di sana!

269
00:20:30,313 --> 00:20:32,065
Kita hampir menabraknya!

270
00:20:32,106 --> 00:20:34,943
