waktu berduaan.

288
00:21:18,861 --> 00:21:20,613
Serius, Chivo. Demi Tuhan.

289
00:21:21,155 --> 00:21:22,156
Sial.

290
00:21:22,490 --> 00:21:23,490
Sara!

291
00:21:35,211 --> 00:21:36,212
Di sana!

292
