431
00:32:51,345 --> 00:32:52,346
Darimana kau?

432
00:32:53,305 --> 00:32:54,306
Dengan Sara.

433
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:57,101
Siapa?
/ Aku akan buat makan malam.

434
00:32:57,142 --> 00:32:58,394
Bir dulu.

435
00:33:02,981 --> 00:33:05,651
Aku sedang tidak mau!
