442
00:35:23,914 --> 00:35:24,748
Sara!

443
00:35:30,796 --> 00:35:31,797
Ibu!

444
00:35:32,464 --> 00:35:33,465
Sara!

445
00:35:34,091 --> 00:35:35,133
Sara, ada apa?

446
00:35:35,175 --> 00:35:36,176
Ibu!

